{"tid":2188591,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"仆街民建聯又嚟害啲老師","createTime":"2020-09-04T10:39:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-04T10:46:44.000Z","uid":277640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c7d7eac6f9fc5ea84d76fecdb8d61b60c37f2a71","tid":2188591,"uid":277640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T10:39:02.000Z","msg":"民建聯晤楊潤雄促呼籲教職員復課前參與檢測<br />\n本地<br />\n發佈時間 2020-09-04 17:24 最後更新時間 2020-09-04 17:22<br />\n<br />\n民建聯立法會議員下午約見教育局長楊潤雄，促請局方再次向全港幼稚園及中小學發通告，<span class=\"red\"><strong>呼籲教職員在復課前參與普及社區檢測計劃</strong></span>，以保障學生健康。張國鈞指，知悉有某些辦學團體抗拒參與自願檢測，亦有校長及教師未有表態是否願意參加，無人希望復課後，校內出現爆發，希望教師能以學童的健康及安全為大前題，參加檢測。政府亦應考慮在復課後約一個月，再次提供檢測計劃，確保校園安全。<br />\n<br />\n鄭泳舜指，會上亦有反映跨境學童復課的問題，他引述楊潤雄說，由於涉及公共交通等問題，有關安排暫時有困難。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.881903.com/news/amp/local/2355762\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Famp%2Flocal%2F2355762&d=HMiOmB7b1AqxO%2BCwCPl1cc0oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=fce5f6db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.881903.com/news/amp/local/2355762</a>"},{"pid":"5f484c4f87869552b0219a196f74d0bc2edcfc65","tid":2188591,"uid":212623,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T10:40:26.000Z","msg":"呃人工都呃得耐啦呢堆教畜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3349403155c61a6d3c7b5a60ff5631711493a6c0","tid":2188591,"uid":214173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T10:42:08.000Z","msg":"視像授課乃大勢所趨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e64b032403b3e94ac2d0b573c7c9c6d13e8cb40a","tid":2188591,"uid":59192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5f484c4f87869552b0219a196f74d0bc2edcfc65","tid":2188591,"uid":212623,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T10:40:26.000Z","msg":"呃人工都呃得耐啦呢堆教畜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},